Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:18.91,SeriesTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(334.133,309.733)\fad(150,270)}Brave{\fscx900} {\r}Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:24.58,SongOP,,0,0,0,,Over a million of them shine with a blue light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:31.26,SongOP,,0,0,0,,The shards of love have scattered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:38.26,SongOP,,0,0,0,,It's brewing in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:41.22,SongOP,,0,0,0,,A storm that you'll confront
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:44.77,SongOP,,0,0,0,,And because I believe in you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:49.69,SongOP,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:53.90,SongOP,,0,0,0,,GO WITH ME Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:57.32,SongOP,,0,0,0,,Courage and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:03.37,SongOP,,0,0,0,,That moment when we join our strength GATHER WAY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.92,SongOP,,0,0,0,,GO WITH ME Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:10.29,SongOP,,0,0,0,,I'd almost forgotten it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:18.64,SongOP,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-0.3\q2}The fiery burning and important PASSIONATE feeling in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The mysterious and vast universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In this universe exists the evil life forms, \Nthe space pirates Geisters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,who've invaded Earth in order to obtain the treasures of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,However, in front of the Geisters who use destruction and plunder as they wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:01:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,a hero appeared, who completely stood in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the cosmic police, Exkaiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the story of Brave Exkaiser and his friends, who fight against evil all around the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:18.87,EpisodeTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(307.168,313.2)}Time Is a Mess
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.6\pos(252.632,124.4)}Great Treasure Exhibition 13F{\alphaFF\fscx400}, {\fscx100\alpha00}Summer Fair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan is so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the Anniversary of Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable that she's late on the Anniversary of Sky Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,At 2:30 we'll watch a movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,at 4 we'll have tea,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and at 5 it's study time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My perfect schedule is falling apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you made a too \Ndetailed time schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be like me and just be like "At afternoon it's playing time!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to become a man who carries Japan on his shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I could make a loose schedule like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of what to wear so I came a little late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:03:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it! About 30 minutes don't even feel like we waited!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are one to talk!\N You were angry just a minute ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an atomic clock that shows the standard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Around the world, people match their country's time to this atomic clock
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and so they can show the exact time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The world's time...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,P-President!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kyuuku department store's mechanism clock disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It was the flower clock that \Ndisappeared, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the mechanism clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The flower clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can find that out by reading papa's newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to wait for the evening paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Today afternoon, starting from the atomic clock of world's standard time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,incidents where rare clocks were stolen from all over the world happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sapporo's clock tower and London's Big Ben are both now lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't only the mechanic clock that disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,According to witnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,they've said that a dinosaur took them, but there's no positive proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Geisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Rare clocks are being targeted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be on alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, since there's a rare clock here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'll dash through a second round!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Thunder Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dash Max?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just slipped a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Those damn Geisters ruined our race again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'll come immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to do the impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, don't be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll beat them up easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Dash Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I, Dash Max, exist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,your evil doings are absolutely unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash Max, answer! Dash Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a payback from the other time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for the time before that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't stop soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,he won't be much of a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more important now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we can sell this much rare \Nclocks at a high price!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I stole most of them, \Nso my share must be the biggest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll obviously get the best share, \Nsince I'm the one who thought of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't even worked that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about me-...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the fighting among yourselves for later and look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Installation of the spare atomic clock has been finished successfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, all the clocks around the world have regained the standard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now who was it that said that there's only one atomic clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I could know there's a spare one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, they're playing dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The clocks would be a treasure, \Nif there's only one of them in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no treasure if two of them exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,... Is what Lord Dino Geist said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to make the other clocks out of order, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This place was safe, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're only stealing clocks... Could it be because today's the Anniversary of Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the mechanic clock of the Kyuuku department store!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But that couldn't be... Since it got stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, if it isn't the atomic clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of the clock museum, \Nit's got everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastards! Don't think you'll get off easy for doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you still want us to pay attention to you! There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Ptera Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sapporo's clock tower and other \Nvarious tourist places-...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry for that. We'll continue the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This piece of news seems to tell something about that recent shock wave...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like clocks have broken all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I flew in a 5 km radius around the race area, but I didn't get any response.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Blue Raker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I went as far as 20 km from the race area, but I couldn't catch a response from Dash Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kouta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All the clocks in the world broke at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be the work of Geisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Our spare atomic clock is broken too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the exact time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When is the 18:00 train arriving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the 17:00 train hasn't arrived yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's going on with that 17:00 train?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I don't know which trains are running at the moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for the 3 o'clock news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie! What do you mean "3 o'clock news"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already dark outside! It's nighttime!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better show our drama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The 3 o'clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,news...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Aiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,are starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief editor, this is all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why we became so busy when there's no clocks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief editor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun is rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Get the manuscripts printed quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief editor, I am getting paid for overtime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have time to think about useless things...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here... The classes were longer than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They were actually shorter than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that tree's shadow \Nis currently in that position...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's 3 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the theory of the sun watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned it in grade school!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected from Mr. Tokuda, you are so educated!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on now, madam! Don't tease me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's expand the scope of our search.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Raker should head west as till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Green Raker should head north.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found out something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But you sure look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a mess now that the clocks are broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't clocks only machines that punctuate time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So why all this just because such things broke...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that clocks are gone, I realized for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that punctuating time is really important!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't know the punctuation, \Nyou just keep on studying or working
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's what makes you tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So clocks are very important, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And those Geisters dare mess with such important things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Blue Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser, I've caught an unidentified energy wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's get rid of those rare clocks already and make Lord Dino Geist delighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:14:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... It's about the time I'll get contacted by the space merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet those humans have now learned the dread of us Geisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You villains!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's the only time you'll be able to laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll laugh as much as I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Sky Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Drill Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you take our capture so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My captures!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash Max! Thank god you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't stop with just stealing clocks from around the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so you dared to steal time from humans \Nand disrupt the peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the stolen clocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky Max, Drill Max! You two should protect Dash Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet Boomerang!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What a horrifying power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Blue Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Green Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Raker Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Twin Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,King Loader!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant Fusion, King Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Left&Right Fusion, Ultra Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra Chain Crusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Blaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you learned your lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky Max, Drill Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's combine and I'll aid too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's impossible in your condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the time to be saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's combine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Max Team, Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Triple Fusion, God Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,God Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,God Cosmic Bomber!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad, let's retreat for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it now, King Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunder Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! The clocks are fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it was Exkaiser and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta, feel at ease. \NThe time has returned to you humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Time has come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:21:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This afternoon at 15:05, the various clocks around the country
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,have returned to normal \Nsimultaneously for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the next news,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the clocks that were stolen around the world were found in faraway mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, the morning paper came only now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's this thick! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... It's just that... How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.09,0:22:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's good that everything solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You were fine even without a clock, mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine even if there's no clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.29,0:22:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but if there's no clock then papa gets busy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best when there's a clock and papa is right next to me. Right, papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:56.23,SongED,,0,0,0,,Faraway wind carries your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:05.32,SongED,,0,0,0,,What could you discover from this excited feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:15.37,SongED,,0,0,0,,Dreams get bigger strongly and fast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:23.00,SongED,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to be who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:31.30,SongED,,0,0,0,,Embrace your enthusiastic heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:39.31,SongED,,0,0,0,,And try walking that path
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.45,0:23:46.32,NextEpisodePreview,,0,0,0,,{\pos(312.512,306.667)}NEXT EPISODE PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Red, blue, yellow, purple and... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I can't say all 7 colors, \Nrainbows are really pretty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.23,0:23:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going on a hiking to the \NRainbow Waterfall today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.63,0:24:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But even Geisters came along with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How horrible! The dam's water is overflowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The town will be filled with water!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.75,0:24:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of Brave Exkaiser,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.23,0:24:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Flood at the Rainbow Waterfall
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.75,0:24:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an alien in your home, too?
